{{nihongo|'''Masaki Minami'''|<U+5357> <U+660C><U+8F1D>|Minami Masaki}} is a Japanese professional baseball pitcher. He was born on January 18, 1989. He is currently playing for the [[Chiba Lotte Marines]] of the NPB.<ref name="baseball-reference">{{cite web|url=http://www.baseball-reference.com/japan/player.cgi?id=minami000mas|title=Masaki Minami  Japanese League Statistics &amp; History - Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=baseball-reference.com|accessdate=2014-01-12}}</ref>

